Cheyenne.Nagle Warren Mansion: Nagle Warren Mansion, also known as Cheyenne YWCA Building, is former residence and YWCA with three buildings located in Cheyenne, Laramie County, Wyoming. The mansion is on the edge of Cheyenne's historic downtown section on Cattle Baron’s Row. It is now a bed and breakfast (B&B) establishment with 12 guest rooms decorated in Victorian West style.
